Class ARLayout

java.lang.Object
  View
      com.magnitude.ARKitapi.ARLayout

public class ARLayout
extends View

ARLayout class implements all the calculation to show POIs correctly on the screen. This should not be modified if you only plan to develop plugins

Author:
Chris Haseman - modified by Magnitude Client.
